----------------

-SnackBar

   steps
   ------
	1. Snackbar snackbar;	//Globally declare snackbar.
	2. View view = findViewById(R.id.activity_main); //under onCreate() method
	3. snackbar = Snackbar.make(view, "Hello Snackbar!", Snackbar.LENGTH_INDEFINITE (or) Snackbar.LENGTH_LONG);
	3.1. this is how we set manually the duration
		- snackbar.setDuration(10000);
		- snackbar.dismiss(); // this is how we provide cancel
	4. snackbar.show();








 Advantage is that dispaly duration of snackbar can be adjusted.
	Snackbar.LENGTH_INDEFINITE// CONTINUOUSLY DISPLAYS untill progreamatically we dismiss it.! 

	steps
